# Nested Lists Complex

## Unordered Lists

- First level item one
- First level item two
  - Second level item A
  - Second level item B
    - Third level item i
    - Third level item ii
      - Fourth level deep nesting
  - Back to second level
- Back to first level
- Another first level

## Ordered Lists

1. First ordered item
2. Second ordered item
   1. Nested ordered A
   2. Nested ordered B
      1. Deep nested one
      2. Deep nested two
   3. Back to nested level
3. Third ordered item

## Mixed List Types

- Unordered parent
  1. Ordered child one
  2. Ordered child two
     - Unordered grandchild
     - Another grandchild
  3. Ordered child three
- Another unordered parent

## Lists With Formatting

- **Bold list item**
- *Italic list item*
- Item with `code` in it
- Item with [link](https://example.com)
- ~~Strikethrough item~~
